ports%20communications%20job%20postings%20he'd%20come%20across%20had%20attracted%20more%20than%201%2C000%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20is%20to%20obviously%20get%20a%20job%20in%20the%20sports%20industry%2C%20but%20realistically%2C%20I%20know%20that%20life%20isn't%20fair%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jones%2C%20who's%20in%20his%2020s%20and%20lives%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20%26quot%3BSo%20at%20this%20point%2C%20I'm%20just%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20job%2C%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22408249e4-3094-4221-b437-25d8a5411960%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20job%20seekers%20are%20coping%20with%20the%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20and%20breaking%20through%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20job%20seekers%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20have%20leaned%20on%20others%20%E2%80%94%20including%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20professional%20contacts%2C%20and%20fellow%20job%20seekers%20%E2%80%94%20for%20support%20and%20solidarity%20during%20their%20job%20searches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoff-job-hunt-struggles-pay-rent-tech-industry-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20by%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%2C%20Ian%20Carter%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20new%20job.%20He%20switched%20to%20a%20month-to-month%20lease%20on%20his%20Redmond%2C%20Washington%2C%20apartment%2C%20but%20eventually%20moved%20to%20Florida%20to%20save%20money%20by%20living%20with%20family%20while%20continuing%20his%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarter%20said%20he's%20connected%20with%20others%20who've%20lost%20their%20jobs%20and%20visits%20the%20private%20%26quot%3BMSFT%20Survivors%26quot%3B%20Facebook%20group%2C%20which%20includes%20people%20who've%20been%20laid%20off%20throughout%20Microsoft's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLayoffs%20kind%20of%20affect%20people%20mentally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carter%2C%20who's%20in%20his%2030s.%20%26quot%3BI've%20reached%20out%20to%20people%20so%20we%20can%20be%20each%20other's%20support%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ian%20Carter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6945540e64858d02d217202c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIan%20Carter%3Cp%3EIan%20Carter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Sriram%20Ramkrishna%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-layoff-job-search-challenges-tech-interviews-software-engineer-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20by%20Intel%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20On%20his%20last%20official%20day%20with%20the%20company%2C%20his%20wife%20also%20lost%20her%20job.%20When%20he%20learned%20the%20news%2C%20his%20mindset%20shifted%20from%20%26quot%3BI'll%20find%20a%20job%20when%20I%20can%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BI'd%20better%20find%20a%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20he's%20struggled%20to%20make%20much%20headway.%20Ramkrishna%20said%20one%20of%20the%20things%20keeping%20him%20going%20is%20the%20support%20of%20his%20former%20Intel%20colleagues%2C%20who%20also%20lost%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20us%20have%20been%20helping%20each%20other%20with%20our%20job%20searches%20%E2%80%94%20sharing%20opportunities%20and%20offering%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ramkrishna%2C%20who's%20in%20his%2050s%20and%20lives%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20we're%20all%20looking%20out%20for%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Martin%2C%20lead%20researcher%20at%20Glassdoor%2C%20said%20uncertainty%20helped%20drive%20this%20year's%20low-fire%2C%20low-hire%20job%20market%2C%20such%20as%20businesses%20navigating%20the%20effects%20of%20tariffs%20and%20AI.%20Terrazas%2C%20the%20independent%20economist%2C%20doesn't%20think%20uncertainty%20will%20fully%20fade%20next%20year%2C%20but%20said%20emp