ce%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20evidence%20that%20someone%20doesn't%20want%20to%20stay%20at%20Compass%20and%20help%20us%20weather%20this%20storm%2C%20say%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Reffkin%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompass-ceo-robert-reffkin-memo-managers-poor-performers-cost-cutting-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDecember%202022%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%20%26quot%3BManaging%20out%20poor%20performers.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20notched%20its%20first%20quarterly%20profit%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20last%20year%2C%20and%20ended%20the%20year%20with%20a%20%24154%20million%20net%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20longer%20focused%20solely%20on%20steadying%20the%20ship%2C%20Reffkin%20has%20turned%20his%20efforts%20to%20unseating%20real%20estate's%20entrenched%20powers%3A%20the%20rulemakers%20that%20determine%20how%20most%20sellers%20market%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20he%20came%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20I%20think%20from%20the%20beginning%20he%20had%20no%20inborn%20reverence%20for%20the%20structure%20or%20the%20power%20centers%20in%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Boero%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20fall%2C%20Reffkin%20unveiled%20what%20he%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bthree-phased%20marketing%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20transform%20Compass.com%20into%20an%20exclusive%20destination%20for%20coveted%20home%20listings.%20When%20a%20typical%20agent%20begins%20working%20with%20a%20seller%2C%20they'll%20usually%20put%20the%20home%20into%20a%20local%20database%20known%20as%20the%20multiple%20listing%20service%2C%20or%20MLS%2C%20which%20distributes%20the%20info%20to%20other%20agents%20and%20home-search%20portals%20like%20Zillow%20or%20Realtor.com.%20This%20may%20sound%20like%20good%20business%20practice%2C%20but%20agents%20also%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20choice%3A%20In%202019%2C%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20passed%20a%20new%20rule%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20agents%20swapping%20home%20listings%20outside%20the%20MLSs.%20Known%20as%20the%20Clear%20Cooperation%20Policy%2C%20it%20dictated%20that%20within%20one%20business%20day%20of%20marking%20a%20home%20publicly%20%E2%80%94%20posting%20about%20it%20on%20Facebook%2C%20planting%20a%20sign%20in%20the%20front%20yard%2C%20advertising%20it%20on%20a%20brokerage's%20website%20%E2%80%94%20an%20agent%20had%20to%20either%20share%20the%20listing%20in%20their%20local%20MLS%20for%20everyone%20to%20see%2C%20or%20face%20potentially%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20NAR%20was%20forced%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-housing-market-homebuying-agents-commissions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettle%20landmark%20class-action%20lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20over%20a%20%3Cem%3Edifferent%20%3C%2Fem%3Eset%20of%20MLS%20rules%20regarding%20agent%20commissions%20%E2%80%94%20costing%20the%20trade%20group%20%24418%20million%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20Compass%20%2457.5%20million%20%E2%80%94%20Reffkin%20says%20he%20experienced%20an%20awakening.%20Why%2C%20he%20wondered%2C%20did%20a%20non-government%20trade%20group%20get%20to%20decide%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20road%20for%20the%20entire%20housing%20market%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20trade%20association%20telling%20investment%20bankers%20how%20to%20run%20their%20business%2C%20how%20to%20serve%20their%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Reffkin%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20just%20not%20right.%20And%20so%20I%20think%20I'm%20looking%20at%20this%20like%2C%20'What%20is%20going%20on%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20NAR%20spokesperson%20says%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20group's%20work%20%26quot%3Bfosters%20a%20competitive%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20pro-consumer%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20its%20members%20have%20a%20say%20on