isk%20of%20crumbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22541e8584-4c5a-4951-a761-9cf8645c90ff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20war%20with%20Zillow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompass'%20move%20also%20represented%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20portals%20like%20Zillow%3A%20The%20biggest%20name%20in%20home%20search%20would%20lose%20its%20luster%20if%20buyers%20knew%20it%20had%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20available%20listings.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Compass%20is%20able%20to%20say%20that%20we%20have%20listings%20that%20Zillow%20doesn't%20have%2C%20then%20people%20would%20search%20Compass%2C%26quot%3B%20Reffkin%20said%20in%20court.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20simple%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Zillow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-new-real-estate-agent-listings-rules-homebuyers-search-homes-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethreatened%20to%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20its%20site%20any%20listings%20that%20weren't%20shared%20with%20everyone%20within%20one%20day%20of%20being%20marketed%20publicly.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20Americans%20are%20struggling%20to%20access%20and%20afford%20housing%2C%20Compass%20wants%20to%20hide%20available%20listings%20from%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Zillow%20spokesperson%20says%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BHidden%20listings%20harm%20consumers%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20smaller%20brokerages%3B%20Zillow's%20standards%20protect%20against%20that%20harm.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-fights-push-brokerages-real-estate-listings-more-exclusive-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esending%20warnings%20to%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20breached%20the%20policy%2C%20allowing%20two%20strikes%20per%20agent%20before%20blocking%20listings%20from%20its%20site.%20Shortly%20before%20enforcement%20took%20effect%20in%20June%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompass-zillow-lawsuit-homebuyers-search-listing-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECompass%20sued%20Zillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20federal%20court%2C%20claiming%20the%20company%20was%20using%20its%20monopoly%20power%20to%20quash%20Compass'%20innovative%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20think%20of%20anything%20else%20in%20our%20entire%20history%20that%20could%20compare%20to%20this%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Steve%20Halpern%2C%20an%20agent%20who%20joined%20Compass%20in%202013.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Robert%20wants%20something%2C%20and%20Robert%20is%20committed%20to%20getting%20something%2C%20he%20usually%20finds%20a%20way%20to%20achieve%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NAR%20and%20Zillow%20make%20for%20convenient%20enemies.%20The%20NAR%2C%20which%20has%20roughly%201.5%20million%20members%20and%20effectively%20governs%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20MLSs%2C%20is%20still%20reeling%20from%20leadership%20upheaval%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuyers-sellers-realtor-agent-commissions-saving-rule-changes-lawsuit-settlement-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettlement%20over%20agent%20commissions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Zillow%20is%20plainly%20disliked%20in%20many%20corners%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20industry.%20The%20search%20giant%20makes%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20its%20money%20by%20selling%20%26quot%3Bleads%26quot%3B%20to%20agents%3A%20When%20you%20click%20the%20buttons%20to%20contact%20an%20agent%20or%20schedule%20a%20tour%2C%20Zillow%20will%20typically%20pass%20along%20your%20contact%20information%20to%20an%20agent%20who%20pays%20a%20fee%20to%20the%20site%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20agent%20who%20actually%20listed%20the%20house%20for%20sale.%20In%20court%2C%20Reffkin%20called%20this%20practice%20%26quot%3Bfree%20riding.%26quot%3B%20In%20his%20estimation%2C%20Zillow%20is%20merely%20profiting%20off%20agents'%20legwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZillow%20knows%20who%20they%20can%20bully%20and%20who%20they%20can't%2C%26quot%3B%20Reffkin%20said%20in%20court.%20Large%20homebuilders%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20regularly%20advertise%20homes%20off%20the%20MLS%20without%20repercussion.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20easy%20to%20bully%20an%20industry%20of%20individual%20agents%20like%20my%20mom%20or%20independent%20contractors%2C%26quot%3B%20Reffkin%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThey%20do%20not%20make%20a%20salary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Zillow%20spokesperson%20says%20the%20company%20invests%20heavily%20in%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20tools%20that%20help%20agents%20grow%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompass%20agents%20may%20be%20Reffkin's%20loudest%20supporters%2C%20but%20not%20all%20are%20on%20board.%20Some%20have%20balked%20at%20his%20crusade%2C%20which%20goes%20against%20what%20many%20in%20the%20industry%20consider%20to%20be%20both%20standard%20practice%20and%20common%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BListings%20belong%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20for%20all%20homebuyers%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Alyssia%20Essig%2C%20a%20Compass%20agent%20in%20the%20Baltimore%20area%2C%20said%20in%20a%20YouTube%20video%20in%20early%20August.%20After%20the%20video%20gained%20traction%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20Reffkin%2C%20and%20they%20debated%20the%20issue%20over%20the%20phone.%20Neither%20changed%20their%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssig%20says%20she%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20leave%20Compass%20%E2%80%94%20she%20loves%20the%20tech%20and%20the%20people.%20But%20the%20push%20toward%20exclusive%20inventory%2C%20she%20tells%20me%2C%20means%20she%20has%20to%20sift%20through%20emails%2C%20text%20messages%2C%20and%20social%20media%20to%20find%20homes%20advertised%20in%20more%20discreet%20channels.%20It's%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20everything%20more%20difficult%2C%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20it's%20already%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224670%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22home%20for%20sale%20century%2021%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6947039264858d02d21735ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223367%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20Compass%20is%20able%20to%20merge%20with%20Anywhere%2C%20the%20combined%20company%20will%20be%20a%20real%20estate%20giant.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20people%20in%20the%20industry%20told%20me%20they'd%20been%20blocked%20on%20LinkedIn%20by%20Reffkin%20after%20they%20pushed%20back%20in%20the%20comments%20of%20his%20social%20media%20posts.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20Shaun%20Michael%20Lewis%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Clearwater%20Properties%2C%20a%20midsize%20real%20estate%20brokerage%20with%2035%20offices%20across%20the%20Mountain%20West.%20Lewis%20says%20he%20understands%20the%20pressures%20to%20grow%20market%20share%2C%20but%20worries%20that%20Reffkin%20will%20drag%20the%20industry%20back%20to%20a%20time%20when%20homes%20were%20more%20difficult%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20him%20on%20TV%20or%20listen%20to%20him%20on%20a%20podcast%2C%20he's%20a%20very%20intelligent%2C%20very%20charming%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20have%20experience%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20you%20understand%20that%20what%20he's%20actually%20saying%20%E2%80%94%20while%20it%20probably%20sounds%20good%20for%20laymen%2C%20the%20consumer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20it's%20just%20bunk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReffkin%20is%20undeterred.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20seen%20him%20back%20down%20from%20a%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20DelPrete%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20opposite.%20He%20will%20double%20down%2C%20triple%20down.%26quot%3B%20The%20pending%20acquisition%20of%20Anywhere%2C%20expected%20to%20close%20late%20next%20year%2C%20would%20add%20more%20than%20170%2C000%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eagents%20to%20Compass%20ranks%2C%20combine%20the%20two%20largest%20brokerages%20by%20sales%20volume%2C%20and%20give%20Reffkin%20more%20power%20to%20mold%20the%20housing%20market%20in%20his%20image.%20In%20key%20markets%20such%20as%20New%20York%20City%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20Washington%2C%20the%20brands%20under%20the%20joint%20entity%20would%20boast%20a%20market%20share%20ranging%20from%2030%25%20to%2050%25%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20T3%20Sixty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20regular%20buyers%2C%20Reffkin's%20vision%20could%20usher%20in%20a%20more%20complicated%20home%20search%3A%20You%20might%20have%20to%20visit%20a%20range%20of%20sites%20to%20unearth%20home%20inventory%2C%20or%20sweat%20over%20whether%20your%20agent%20is%20actually%20showing%20you%20everything%20out%20there.%20Reffkin%20argues%20that%20this%20fight%20isn't%20actually%20about%20%26quot%3Bhidden%26quot%3B%20home%20listings%20at%20all%3A%20It's%20about%20marketing%20homes%20publicly%20without%20quickly%20sharing%20them%20in%20the%20MLS%20and%20Zillow.%20Sellers%20and%20their%20agents%2C%20he%20says%2C%20should%20have%20the%20choice%20to%20promote%20their%20homes%20however%20they%20please%2C%20without%20fear%20of%20getting%20dinged%20for%20price%20cuts%20or%20days%20on%20market.%20In%20his%20dream%20scenario%2C%20the%20home%20search%20might%20not%20be%20all%20that%20complicated%3A%20In%20places%20where%20his%20company%20has%20a%20strong%20presence%2C%20you%20could%20just%20go%20to%20Compass.com%20and%20find%20houses%20there%20instead%20of%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20guarantee%20he%20will%20come%20close%20to%20that%20goal.%20Because%20agents%20are%20independent%20contractors%2C%20Reffkin%20can't%20force%20them%20to%20adopt%20his%20three-phased%20marketing%20strategy.%20The%20Anywhere%20deal%20could%20face%20regulatory%20scrutiny%20or%20fall%20apart%20for%20other%20reasons%2C%20and%20if%20it%20goes%20through%2C%20Compass%20will%20end%20up%20with%20more%20than%20%242%20billion%20in%20additional%20debt.%20The%20court%20battle%20with%20Zillow%20is%20another%20question%20mark.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20take%20out%20the%20king%2C%26quot%3B%20Jack%20Miller%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20T3%20Sixty%2C%20told%20me%20in%20September.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20week%20is%20for%20Zillow%2C%20I%20still%20think%20they're%20such%20a%20powerful%20player.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Zillow's%20posturing%2C%20Compass'%20website%20is%20home%20to%20thousands%20of%20listings%20that%20can't%20be%20found%20anywhere%20else.%20Its%20agent%20count%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high.%20Other%20big%20brokerages%20are%20readying%20their%20own%20private%20databases%20of%20listings%2C%20prepping%20for%20Reffkin's%20vision%20to%20become%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20entirely%20clear%20what%20a%20loss%20would%20mean%20for%20the%20company%20and%20Reffkin.%20When%20I%20meet%20him%20at%20Compass'%20midtown%20Manhattan%20headquarters%2C%20I%20ask%20a%20version%20of%20this%20question%3A%20What%20if%20the%20fight%20doesn't%20go%20your%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20can%20finish%20my%20next%20sentence%2C%20he%20interjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20never%20give%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20correspondent%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompass-ceo-robert-reffkin-zillow-war-homebuying-real-estate-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766309221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6945b5d104eda4732f2de871%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompass-ceo-robert-reffkin-zillow-war-homebuying-real-estate-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Robert%20Reffkin%20is%20one%20of%20real%20estate's%20most%20polarizing%20