Fny-population-growth-see-lower-hudson-valley-area-resident-numbers%2F83669399007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopulation%20is%20booming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20rents%20and%20home%20prices%20haven't%20risen%20nearly%20as%20fast%20as%20in%20other%20cities%20in%20the%20region%20and%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20plans%20to%20fulfill%20its%20goal%20of%20adding%2011%2C000%20units%20in%20about%2032%20buildings%20in%20several%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Freal-estate%2Fnyc-new-rochelle-lower-rent-e7695ded%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20the%20city's%20housing%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2037%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%20The%20mayor%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20city%20is%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20way%20to%20its%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20efforts%20are%20showing%20signs%20of%20success.%20Median%20rents%20in%20New%20Rochelle%20rose%20by%20just%207%25%20between%202017%20and%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pew.org%2Fen%2Fresearch-and-analysis%2Farticles%2F2023%2F04%2F17%2Fmore-flexible-zoning-helps-contain-rising-rents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Pew%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Apartment%20List%20data.%20That's%20compared%20to%20a%2031%25%20median%20rent%20increase%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20the%20city%20has%20supercharged%20housing%20construction%20by%20overhauling%20zoning%20laws%2C%20streamlining%20environmental%20review%2C%20and%20offering%20new%20tax%20breaks%20to%20developers.%20The%20city%20has%20focused%20on%20revitalizing%20its%20downtown%20by%20building%20homes%20on%20underutilized%20commercial%20and%20parking%20lots%20near%20rail%20and%20bus%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20weren't%20tearing%20down%20homes.%20We%20weren't%20tearing%20down%20existing%20apartment%20buildings%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramos-Herbert%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20this%20fall%20with%20