e%20companies%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-tells-visa-holders-stamp-leave-us-return-delays-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20and%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20legal%20counsels%20have%20advised%20staffers%20requiring%20a%20visa%20stamp%20to%20re-enter%20the%20US%20not%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20due%20to%20extended%20processing%20times%20resulting%20from%20the%20new%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsular%20offices%20began%20conducting%20online%20presence%20reviews%20for%20H-1B%20applicants%20on%20December%2015%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20the%20only%20ones%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228833aa6a-6d79-4e82-b686-65fe714c6158%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20does%20the%20social%20media%20reviews%20impact%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20US%20is%20requiring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-to-review-h-1b-applicants-social-media-state-dept-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visa%20applicants%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20their%20dependents%20to%20make%20their%20social%20media%20accounts%20public%20so%20consular%20officers%20can%20review%20their%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-industries-employ-h1-b-visa-holders-charts-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visa%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20enables%20companies%20to%20temporarily%20employ%20foreign%20skilled%20workers%20in%20specialized%20roles.%20Data%20collected%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Labor%20showed%20that%20almost%2050%25%20of%20H-1B%20applications%20are%20in%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%2C%20scientific%2C%20and%20technical%26quot%3B%20fields.%20They%20are%20commonly%20relied%20on%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20said%20international%20students%20and%20exchange%20visitors%20are%20also%20subject%20to%20%26quot%3Bonline%20presence%26quot%3B%20reviews%2C%20specifically%20for%20F%2C%20M%2C%20and%20J%20non-immigrant%20visa%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20memo%2C%20Google's%20legal%20counsel%20told%20staffers%20that%20lengthy%20processing%20delays%20were%20affecting%20H-1B%2C%20H-4%2C%20F%2C%20J%2C%20and%20M%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e6d0d22-7d19-431d-a132-53de7d89a7c0%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20US%20is%20reviewing%20social%20media%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20agencies%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20enforcing%20stricter%20and%20more%20restrictive%20immigration%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Trump%20issued%20an%20executive%20order%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20immigration%20screening.%20It%20was%20meant%20to%20protect%20American%20citizens%20from%20those%20the%20administration%20says%20%26quot%3Bintend%20to%20commit%20terrorist%20attacks%2C%20threaten%20our%20national%20security%2C%20espouse%20hateful%20ideology%2C%20or%20otherwise%20exploit%20the%20immigration%20laws%20for%20malevolent%20purposes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20expanded%20upon%20that%20executive%20order%20in%20June%20and%20then%20again%20this%20week.%20Combined%2C%20those%20subsequent%20orders%20partially%20or%20fully%20restrict%20entry%20for%20citizens%20from%2025%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20also%20began%20charging%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-h-1b-visa-fee-silicon-valley-tech-hiring-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24100%2C000%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20new%20H-1B%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cast%20the%20fee%20as%20a%20corrective.%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%20H-1B%20system%20had%20strayed%20from%20its%20original%20purpose%20of%20filling%20high-skilled%20worker%20shortages%20and%20was%20instead%20being%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%20exploited%20to%20replace%2C%20rather%20than%20supplement%2C%20American%20workers%20with%20lower-paid%2C%20lower-skilled%20labor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20announcement%20about%20the%20social%20media%20checks%20on%20December%203%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20said%20the%20changes%20were%20meant%20to%20increase%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20US%20visa%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%20not%20a%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20State%20Department%20told%20Business%20Insider%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BIn%20every%20visa%20case%2C%20we%20will%20take%20the%20time%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20an%20applicant%20does%20not%20pose%20a%20risk%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217be1f8f-a528-494a-b1aa-9e9bc63e8974%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20do%20(and%20not%20do)%20if%20you%20are%20affected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20be%20tempting%20to%20delete%20your%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20that%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20firm%20Davis%20Wright%20Tremaine%20advised%20in%20a%20post%20on%20its%20website%20that%20visa%20applicants%20should%20review%20their%20social%20media%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20no%20information%20that%20might%20contradict%20the%20details%20submitted%20in%20their%20applications.%20The%20law%20firm%20Duane%20Morris%20advised%20against%20deleting%20posts%20or%20profiles.%20If%20an%20immigration%20official%20notices%2C%20it%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20evasive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20a%20visa%20applicant%20can%20do%20is%20stay%20in%20the%20US%20during%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaun%20Foster%2C%20an%20immigration%20attorney%20who%20owns%20the%20firm%20PampaninFoster%20based%20in%20Cambridge%2C%20Mass.%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20message%20that%20he%20is%20encouraging%20clients%20on%20H-1B%20visas%20to%20play%20it%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20continued%20to%20emphasize%20generally%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20moving%20forward%20in%20working%20toward%20your%20immigration%20goals%20from%20within%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20much%20better%20positioned%2C%20as%20immigration%20counsel%2C%20to%20more%20strongly%20assist%20and%20guide%20people%20from%20within%20the%20US.%20There's%20less%20control%20when%20you%20start%20integrating%20international%20consular%20elements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b145cdd7-db64-4a35-a209-8d5f50ab780a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20companies%20are%20reacting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Google%20and%20Apple%20have%20already%20advised%20some%20employees%20on%20visas%20not%20to%20travel%20outside%20the%20US%20due%20to%20delays%20at%20embassies%20stemming%20from%20the%20increased%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20be%20aware%20that%20some%20US%20Embassies%20and%20Consulates%20are%20experiencing%20significant%20visa%20stamping%20appointment%20delays%2C%20currently%20reported%20as%20up%20to%2012%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Google's%20legal%20counsel%20wrote%20in%20a%20memo%20sent%20on%20Thursday%20to%20employees%20on%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFragomen%2C%20a%20law%20firm%20that%20represents%20Apple%2C%20similarly%20said%20in%20a%20memo%20sent%20last%20week%20to%20some%20visa%20holders%20at%20the%20company%20that%20they%20should%20refrain%20from%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20recent%20updates%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20unpredictable%2C%20extended%20delays%20when%20returning%20to%20the%20US%2C%20we%20strongly%20recommend%20that%20employees%20without%20a%20valid%20H-1B%20visa%20stamp%20avoid%20international%20travel%20for%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20memos%20were%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20companies%20and%20many%20others%20are%20still%20smarting%20after%20Trump%20imposed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22