0for%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Epstein%20files%20and%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20in%20July%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20to%20fear.%26quot%3B%20In%20multiple%20interviews%20before%20the%20latest%20release%2C%20Tucker%20has%20denied%20any%20knowledge%20of%20criminal%20activity.%20Jagger%20has%20not%20responded%20publicly.%20Ferguson%20has%20said%20she%20cut%20ties%20with%20Epstein%20after%20his%20conviction.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20from%20Epstein%20files.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6946ba5d04eda4732f2dee5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%20in%20a%20pool.%3Cp%3EDepartment%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227da2830c-aa1d-45c5-b4f4-e0b0f5c45e56%5C%22%3E2.%20Redactions%20draw%20criticisms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department's%20release%20drew%20criticism%20from%20some%20victims%20and%20Democrats%20for%20its%20heavy%20redactions%20and%20limited%20initial%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20entire%20documents%20were%20obscured%20by%20black%20boxes%2C%20including%20one%20119-page%20file.%20The%20DOJ%20has%20attributed%20its%20delay%20in%20producing%20all%20the%20documents%20by%20the%20December%2019%20deadline%20in%20part%20to%20its%20duty%20to%20safeguard%20the%20personal%20information%20of%20victims%20and%20other%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22994%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Redacted%20documents%20from%20the%20Epstein%20files%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6946c74c04eda4732f2dee93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EImage%20with%20redactions%20from%20the%20Epstein%20files%3Cp%3EScreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22044aeccf-fe0f-4330-8a1c-9299b7666526%5C%22%3E3.%201996%20co