0would%20complete%20the%20large%20family%20I%20also%20always%20wanted.%20Perfection%20would%20become%20what%20it%20was%20meant%20to%20be%2C%20a%20foolish%20ideal%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20reality%20to%20strive%20for%20at%20all%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222614%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20birthday%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6920988babd5e944effb3f72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221714%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20grandmother%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20terminal%20cancer.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20repeated%20exactly%20what%20I%20knew.%20My%20kids%20had%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-coord-sets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ematching%20outfits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20picture-perfect%20Christmas%20cards%2C%20and%20all%20the%20things%20perfection%20required.%20I%20would%20clean%20and%20exercise%20until%20I%20reached%20the%20point%20of%20exhaustion.%20I%20worked%20out%20through%20all%20four%20pregnancies%20and%20directly%20after.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recall%20throwing%20a%20birthday%20party%20for%20my%20son.%20He%20was%20turning%203%20or%204.%20Someone%20commented%20on%20how%20great%20I%20looked.%20%26quot%3BNicole%20makes%20sure%20everything%20is%20always%20perfect%2C%26quot%3B%20someone%20else%20said.%20I%20reveled%20in%20the%20praise.%20Gram%20heard%20the%20comment%20and%20smiled.%20We%20shared%20a%20common%20bond.%20When%20one%20of%20us%20inched%20closer%20to%20it%2C%20the%20other%20one%20felt%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd3f3fe5-1358-4467-b0f4-0a4dd0e63216%5C%22%3EThen%20my%20grandmother%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparental-burnout-millennial-most-exhausted-generation-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexhaustion%20of%20parenting%3C%2Fa%