0every%20other%20holiday%20tradition%2C%20including%20festive%20train%20rides%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusy-family-simple-modest-low-key-christmas-kids-are-fine-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emall%20photos%20with%20Santa%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20when%20my%20kids%20were%20young%2C%20the%20weekends%20between%20Thanksgiving%20and%20New%20Year's%20were%20packed%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeaningful-holiday-christmas-tradition-kids-teens-look-forward-to-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eholiday%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leaving%20me%20exhausted%20and%20counting%20the%20days%20until%20they%20went%20back%20to%20school%20in%20January.%20The%20elation%20of%20Santa's%20arrival%20was%20paired%20with%20too-early%20wakeups%20and%20too%20many%20presents%20to%20assemble%20late%20at%20night.%20I%20loved%20seeing%20the%20joy%20in%20their%20eyes%20when%20they%20opened%20that%20LEGO%20set%20or%20butterfly-growing%20kit%2C%20but%20man%2C%20it%20was%20exhausting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20tween%20years%2C%20which%20had%20me%20begging%20for%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20to%20join%20me%20on%20our%20annual%20drive%20through%20the%20neighborhood%20to%20look%20for%20the%20best%20holiday%20lights.%20These%20were%20the%20years%20when%20everything%20seemed%20like%20forced%20family%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20heavy%20bribery%20(or%20light%20threats)%20to%20get%20anyone%20to%20come%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20next%20to%20a%20Christmas%20tree%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20children.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6942f459832e0ef1ead666bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20her%20kids%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kate%20Loweth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2