Bfrom%20time%20to%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20are%20necessary%20to%20prevent%20Russia%20from%20interfering%20with%20its%20training%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20certain%20location%20data%20from%20getting%20out%2C%20the%20school%20doesn't%20allow%20photos%20and%20videos%20that%20might%20reveal%20where%20its%20facilities%20are%20based.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20has%20been%20mentioned%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-military-now-fighting-war-bloggers-after-wagner-group-mutiny-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%20military%20bloggers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20influential%20pro-war%20accounts%20that%20often%20circulate%20operational%20details%20and%20commentary%20to%20large%20audiences.%20Though%20they%20are%20typically%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20war%2C%20they%20are%20also%20sometimes%20critical%20of%20Russia's%20performance%20and%20dispute%20some%20of%20its%20defense%20ministry's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20figures%20stand%20in%20an%20open%20field%20beside%20a%20launcher%20with%20a%20grey%20winged%20drone%20in%20the%20air%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6942b18404eda4732f2daa6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrone%20schools%20say%20they're%20targets%20for%20Russia.%3Cp%3EIvan%20Antypenko%2FSuspilne%20Ukraine%2FJSC%20%26quot%3BUA%3APBC%26quot%3B%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERybar%2C%20a%20media%20outlet%20with%201.5%20million%20Telegram%20subscribers%2C%20listed%20Dronarium%20as%20an%20example%20of%20Ukraine's%20drone%20training%20efforts.%20The%20UK%20has%20sanctioned%20Rybar%2C%20initially%20presented%20as%20a%20milblogger%20but%20actually%20a%20partially%20Russian%20government-sponsored%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-offers-10m-for-information-on-russian-rybar-blog-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D